parameters: (He looks at a advertisment about how anyone can be a Knight.)
\n<Oldman>Look what you did you broke my storage robot...
\n<Oldman>Oh, how am I gonna unload this truck now...
I can fix it for you!
Let me make it up to you!
I can fix it for you!
Let me make it up to you!
\n<Adam>Yeah, I helped out this nice old man and he gave me some food.
\n<Adam>Im sorry for getting upset and running away.
\n<Sabrina>I know I can get a little heated sometimes...
\n<Sabrina>So...What kind of goodies did the oldman give you?
\n<Adam>Uhhh, looks like a bunch of meat pies and some sausage links.
\n<Adam>Looks like I wondered to the Neon Plaza.
\n<Adam>Yeah, call you in a bit. Imma search which bus to take home.
(Adam hangs up. He checks his phone and sees which bus he needs to take. He calls Sabrina.)
\n<Adam>Hey, there is a bus stop nearby
\n<Adam>Well, better check if I have change before I head over.
(Adam takes out his wallet to search for change. Suddenly a imp snatches it.)
